2026-04-29T06:31:00.1434316Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1435899Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1437914Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1439349Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1440575Z 20    -->
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1441888Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1444224Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:5-81
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1446109Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1446987Z 22    <!--
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1447528Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1448171Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1449054Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1449766Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1450474Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1451175Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1451884Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1452596Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1453537Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1454215Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1454755Z 33    -->
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1455313Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1456154Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-04-29T06:31:00.1456983Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
