2026-04-29T06:31:00.2679466Z 12    <!--
2026-04-29T06:31:00.2679735Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-29T06:31:00.2680000Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-29T06:31:00.2680593Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-29T06:31:00.2680853Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-29T06:31:00.2681141Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
